CBMappers - a collection of programs to extract PNG images from the game files
created by the citybuilding games Caesar 3, Pharaoh, and Zeus
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

============
Requirements
------------

The programs require libpng and libz to be installed.

===========
Compilation
-----------
To compile these programs, simply type:

make

This will build three command-line programs, one for each of the supported
games:

  * c3mapper
  * pharaohmapper
  * zeusmapper

After compilation, you can move these programs to wherever you please.

================
